title: Ukraine: Russians withdraw from around Kharkiv, batter east - The Associated Press
content: Ukraine: Russians withdraw from around Kharkiv, batter east  The Associated PressView Full Coverage on Google News
description: KYIV, Ukraine (AP) — Russian troops were withdrawing from around Ukraine’s second-largest city after bombarding it for weeks, the Ukrainian military said Saturday, as Kyiv and Moscow's forces engaged in a grinding battle  for the country’s eastern industrial heartland.
